@eric-wieser I do not find any instances of `Vadd`. For `vAdd`, should there be parity with `hSMul` as an exception?

Currently there are some [Set.vAddAssocClass](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Set/Pointwise/SMul.html#Set.vAddAssocClass) that should be renamed to `vadd` like in [Finset.vaddAssocClass](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Data/Finset/Pointwise.html#Finset.vaddAssocClass). hVAdd should probably stay in parallel to hSMul.
